        "text": "10–15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Paul and Silas sent away to Berea. Noble character of the Bereans. The Jews from Thessalonica follow after Paul, and by reason of their enmity he is conducted to Athens",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
