        "text": "third",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " division of Macedonia, about sixty miles from Thessalonica; its modern name is ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "Verria. Went into the synagogue",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
