            "text": "Verria. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cmt_word",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Went into the synagogue",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". No amount of ill usage from the Jews could weaken St. Paul's love for \"his brethren, his kinsmen according to the flesh\" (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Romans 9:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "); and no amount of danger or suffering could check his zeal in preaching the gospel of Christ. Acts 17:10",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
